1. Set the keyboard in azerty. Follow the instructions in:
https://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/tutoriel/configurer_le_clavier#bug_du_clavier_qui_repasse_en_qwerty_a_chaque_demarrage_sous_certaines_versions_recentes

2. Install i3 gaps:
https://github.com/Airblader/i3/wiki/Compiling-&-Installing

3. Install feh viewer:
sudo apt-get install feh

4. Copy the gnome-terminal conf file
.gconf/apps/gnome-terminal/profiles/Default/%gconf.xml

5. Set the background file at:
/usr/share/backgrounds/warty-final-ubuntu.png

6. Set the sound startup time at:
/usr/share/sounds/ubuntu/stereo/system-ready.ogg

